msgid "A MaxCompute project with valid Access ID / Access Key."
msgstr "需要一个可用的 MaxCompute 项目，并准备有效的 Access ID / Access Key。"

msgid ""
"Align ``pdf_path``, ``page_number``, ``chunk_text``, and ``embedding`` "
"column types."
msgstr ""
"对齐 ``pdf_path``、``page_number``、``chunk_text`` 和 ``embedding`` 的列"
"类型。"

msgid "Applicable scenarios"
msgstr "适用场景"

msgid "Background"
msgstr "背景信息"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Bailian ``embed()`` returns a JSON string such as ``{\"data\": "
"[{\"embedding\": [...]}], ...}``. Convert it to a flat float-array JSON "
"string so downstream retrieval and similarity jobs can read the vector "
"column directly."
msgstr ""
"百炼 ``embed()`` 返回形如 ``{{\"data\": [{{\"embedding\": [...]}}], ...}}"
"`` 的 JSON 字符串。将其转换为扁平浮点数组 JSON 字符串，便于下游检索和相似"
"度计算任务直接读取向量列。"

msgid ""
"Calling MaxCompute managed embedding models requires Model Compute "
"Service to host inference traffic."
msgstr "调用 MaxCompute 托管 Embedding 模型需要模型计算服务承载推理流量。"

msgid "Cause"
msgstr "原因"

msgid ""
"Configure ODPS credentials, OSS access, and the embedding model. Replace "
"all placeholder values with your project-specific settings."
msgstr ""
"配置 ODPS 凭证、OSS 访问参数和 Embedding 模型。请将所有占位符替换为你自己"
"的项目配置。"

msgid "Contact the administrator to enable the DPE engine."
msgstr "联系管理员开通 DPE 引擎。"

msgid "Core workflow"
msgstr "核心处理流程"

msgid "DPE is not enabled for the project."
msgstr "项目未开通 DPE。"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

msgid "Document knowledge base RAG question answering."
msgstr "文档知识库 RAG 问答。"

msgid "Duplicate document and near-duplicate paragraph detection."
msgstr "重复文档与近似段落检测。"

msgid "Enterprise document classification and clustering."
msgstr "企业文档分类与聚类分析。"

msgid "Environment setup"
msgstr "环境准备"

msgid "Issue"
msgstr "问题"

msgid ""
"Make sure ``ODPS_ENDPOINT`` and ``options.session.gu_quota_name`` use the"
" same region."
msgstr "确认 ``ODPS_ENDPOINT`` 和 ``options.session.gu_quota_name`` 使用同一地域。"

msgid ""
"MaxFrame reads PDFs through OSS file mount, which requires a configured "
"Role ARN."
msgstr "MaxFrame 通过 OSS 文件挂载读取 PDF，需要配置 Role ARN。"

msgid "Open a MaxFrame session on DPE:"
msgstr "在 DPE 上打开 MaxFrame session："

msgid "PDF Text Parsing and Bailian Embedding"
msgstr "PDF 文本解析和百炼 Embedding"

msgid "PDF parsing UDFs and ``apply_chunk`` run on DPE."
msgstr "PDF 解析 UDF 和 ``apply_chunk`` 需要在 DPE 上执行。"

msgid ""
"Papers, contracts, research reports, product manuals, white papers, and "
"other PDF files carry a large amount of unstructured business knowledge. "
"Raw PDFs often have diverse layouts, varying lengths, and no semantic "
"splitting, which makes them hard to use directly for semantic retrieval, "
"RAG question answering, document classification, and other downstream "
"scenarios."
msgstr ""
"论文、合同、研究报告、产品手册、白皮书等 PDF 是企业和研究机构常见的文档"
"载体，承载着大量非结构化业务知识。原始 PDF 版式多样、长度不一、缺少语义"
"切分，难以直接用于语义检索、RAG 问答、文档分类等下游场景。"

msgid "Persist the processed chunks and embeddings to MaxCompute."
msgstr "将处理后的文本片段和 Embedding 持久化到 MaxCompute。"

msgid ""
"Pre-filter unreadable PDFs, or catch exceptions in the UDF and skip "
"failed files."
msgstr "预先过滤不可读 PDF，或在 UDF 中捕获异常并跳过失败文件。"

msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "前提条件"

msgid ""
"Provide PDF paths relative to the OSS bucket. The UDF mounts the bucket "
"to ``/mnt/oss`` and opens each file as ``/mnt/oss/<pdf_path>``."
msgstr ""
"提供 PDF 在 OSS bucket 下的相对路径。UDF 会将 bucket 挂载到 ``/mnt/oss``"
"，并以 ``/mnt/oss/<pdf_path>`` 的形式打开文件。"

msgid "RAM role is misconfigured."
msgstr "RAM 角色配置不正确。"

msgid "Requirement"
msgstr "条件"

msgid "Semantic retrieval over papers, contracts, and research reports."
msgstr "论文、合同、研报的语义检索。"

msgid "Solution"
msgstr "解决方案"

msgid "Source PDFs are uploaded to a target OSS bucket."
msgstr "已将原始 PDF 上传至目标 OSS bucket。"

msgid "Step 1. Prepare PDF paths"
msgstr "步骤 1：准备 PDF 路径"

msgid "Step 2. Parse PDFs and split into chunks"
msgstr "步骤 2：解析 PDF 并切片"

msgid "Step 3. Generate embeddings with Bailian"
msgstr "步骤 3：调用百炼生成 Embedding"

msgid "Step 4. Convert embedding JSON"
msgstr "步骤 4：转换 Embedding JSON"

msgid "Step 5. Write the result table"
msgstr "步骤 5：写入结果表"

msgid ""
"Text feature asset construction for retrieval, analytics, and data "
"feedback loops."
msgstr "面向检索、分析和数据闭环的文本特征资产沉淀。"

msgid "The PDF file is corrupted or encrypted."
msgstr "PDF 文件损坏或已加密。"

msgid ""
"The UDF has a single responsibility: use ``pymupdf`` to extract page text"
" and ``RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter`` to split by paragraph and "
"sentence boundaries. The output schema is ``pdf_path``, ``page_number``, "
"and ``chunk_text``."
msgstr ""
"UDF 职责单一：使用 ``pymupdf`` 抽取页面文本，并通过 ``"
"RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter`` 按段落和句子边界切分。输出 schema 为 ``"
"pdf_path``、``page_number`` 和 ``chunk_text``。"

msgid "The quota and MaxCompute project are in different regions."
msgstr "Quota 与 MaxCompute 项目不在同一地域。"

msgid ""
"This best practice shows how to run a distributed PDF preprocessing "
"pipeline on MaxFrame and the MaxCompute DPE engine: extract text from "
"PDFs, split the text into semantic chunks, generate sentence embeddings "
"with the Bailian ``text-embedding-v4`` model, and write the resulting "
"feature table back to MaxCompute."
msgstr ""
"本最佳实践演示如何基于 MaxFrame 和 MaxCompute DPE 引擎运行分布式 PDF "
"预处理流水线：抽取 PDF 正文文本、切分为语义片段、调用百炼 ``text-"
"embedding-v4`` 模型生成句向量，并将结果特征表写回 MaxCompute。"

msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "常见问题排查"

msgid ""
"Use ``read_odps_model`` to load the public Bailian ``text-embedding-v4`` "
"model from MaxCompute and generate embeddings for the ``chunk_text`` "
"column in batch. The embedding call is fully managed by MaxCompute Model "
"Compute Service."
msgstr ""
"通过 ``read_odps_model`` 从 MaxCompute 加载百炼公开 ``text-embedding-v4``"
" 模型，并对 ``chunk_text`` 列批量生成向量。Embedding 调用由 MaxCompute "
"模型计算服务托管完成。"

msgid "Verify ``role_arn`` and confirm the RAM role has OSS read permission."
msgstr "检查 ``role_arn``，并确认 RAM 角色已具备 OSS 读取权限。"

msgid "When the job is finished, release the MaxFrame session:"
msgstr "作业完成后，释放 MaxFrame session："

msgid "Write-table failure or column-type error"
msgstr "写表失败或列类型报错"

msgid "``Engine DPE not available``"
msgstr ""

msgid "``OSS access denied``"
msgstr ""

msgid "``apply_chunk`` dtypes do not match the target schema."
msgstr "``apply_chunk`` 的 dtypes 与目标表 schema 不一致。"

msgid "``gu_quota`` unavailable"
msgstr "``gu_quota`` 不可用"

msgid "``pymupdf`` fails to read a PDF"
msgstr "``pymupdf`` 读取 PDF 失败"

